    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/37695671de70c539511991c4d8f458c2.poster.avif?t=1752495140\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/37695671de70c539511991c4d8f458c2.webm?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/37695671de70c539511991c4d8f458c2.mp4?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在DunDun VR中体验多种多样的景色，从血红炎热的Goab沙漠，到阴暗潮湿的1隧道，再到神秘的实验室……更多的神奇景象等你来发现。与奇怪的物品互动，机密钥匙，蠕动眼球，还有大大的按钮。将你自己沉浸于这一段短小却又甜美的体验中，享受宁静的背景音轨，别忘了收集蛋蛋噢！！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>短小精悍的超现实VR体验<br></li><li>部分固定路线、部分自由探索（传送1或自由行动）<br></li><li>原版音轨<br></li><li>与奇特的物品、大大的按钮和机密的钥匙互动<br></li><li>收集蛋蛋<br></li><li>游玩时间：20-30分钟</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天空之鲸</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/7664e9f8e9039d955600a0486f11d3c1.poster.avif?t=1752495140\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/7664e9f8e9039d955600a0486f11d3c1.webm?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/7664e9f8e9039d955600a0486f11d3c1.mp4?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>由你来决定这只可怜的飞行巨兽的命运！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >决胜三分！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/58f8984089d3335e116dc9415f205161.poster.avif?t=1752495140\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/58f8984089d3335e116dc9415f205161.webm?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/58f8984089d3335e116dc9415f205161.mp4?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>哇哦，砰！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参与选秀竞赛</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/ad1f116c0a3cc284b47764852c395774.poster.avif?t=1752495140\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/ad1f116c0a3cc284b47764852c395774.webm?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/ad1f116c0a3cc284b47764852c395774.mp4?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>大大的眼睛在看着你……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超高速！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/6c414698f1d09af2782c20ccad675efe.poster.avif?t=1752495140\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/6c414698f1d09af2782c20ccad675efe.webm?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695870/extras/6c414698f1d09af2782c20ccad675efe.mp4?t=1752495140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>将一切留在身后。",
